    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is acknowledged and accepted based on the strong inter-solver ensemble agreement across three independent FEA platforms, which the team judges to provide confidence functionally equivalent to multi-condition experimental testing. The normalized error of 0.61 is well within the E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criterion. The model is accepted for use in the 510(k) submission.",
